-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
Commands that all Samurai have access to.
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

"sams"     = Gives a listing of all the Samurai on.

"schat"    = Allows you to talk on the Guild line.

"eschat"   = Allows you to emote on the Guild line.

"myhonor"  = Gives you your current Honor ranking.

"pledge"   = Changes your Giri (guild title) on the Sam who.

"wimpy"    = Now null. You gotta love me!

"sambug"   = Allows you to report any Samurai bugs.


-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
